{"tid":967510,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 波、馬、六合彩 邊樣最唔靠運氣","createTime":"2019-01-03T14:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T04:12:50.000Z","uid":15831,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"314f9db25d8e2e282e84954a32f5db4c0aecc0f3","tid":967510,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"六合彩 &mdash; 根本每場獨立機率， 話有數據睇都知on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波 &mdash; 教練 / 假波 / 主客 / 陣容，賽前有好多難量化既變數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n馬 &mdash; 天氣 / 場地 / 馬既體質 / 騎師， 變數多但睇落有組合可以量化咁做統計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁既話可唔可以話賭馬係最唔靠運， 可以靠分析/ 數據去度 提高贏既機會 <br />\n當然唔係話馬會出面啲呀叔拎份馬經就當係<br />\n依家 Big Data / AI 禁進步<br />\n賭馬呢種賭博用數據去賭有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知三樣出面都有大把人做緊<br />\n純粹想討論下邊樣賭博最有機會用數據至少同馬會打個和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 25 歲 （破產）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e1e5a1412747815722f8f6ee74875b091d6a42","tid":967510,"uid":149323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"一定係賭馬"},{"pid":"d22448bee2536e7a879e6b7b4e99f1106fdefa18","tid":967510,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:17:41.000Z","msg":"仲有一點係馬既變數似乎無波禁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n落場砌臨場變數無得講， 但場次 騎師 天氣 呢啲應該比較大影響同容易量化到？ <br />\n會唔會有一啲方法可以收集到然後統計 back test 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1c99a76eb3c3eb845f658e22fe8db0e963b220","tid":967510,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4e1e5a1412747815722f8f6ee74875b091d6a42","tid":967510,"uid":149323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"一定係賭馬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:18:00.000Z","msg":"點解咁講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  學嘢"},{"pid":"1165b4efa743991adec5ab2951f73729e0b44f44","tid":967510,"uid":125976,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"馬都可以係騎師做假，而且既得利益者係啲超有錢嘅正當商人，你根本唔會知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9f650b7426d1ff0680ef33ad8b2a1590b9cf60","tid":967510,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"024b975fbddd930d4bc9788a138e773f173b2375","tid":967510,"uid":222316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T18:03:11.000Z","msg":"切勿沉迷賭博<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929203a3ff3c64e42957f995013c45b29833509f","tid":967510,"uid":68457,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T01:03:52.000Z","msg":"馬太多人為因素<br />\n馬房/馬主去唔去馬 好多時根本無法預料"},{"pid":"f055003d50c053a935ae6aca83a5cfa9086c1c1d","tid":967510,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"樓主 唔好諗咁多 比心機搵份工 收工打下炮就算 再諗落去你會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74431a969df5e5e47bc9c3d92c08d433b4fa231","tid":967510,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"馬幾時發癲真係無得估"},{"pid":"9520b921ba04f6d6a2a82c7cd9f4d26b4ce01238","tid":967510,"uid":125976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f055003d50c053a935ae6aca83a5cfa9086c1c1d","tid":967510,"uid":127118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"樓主 唔好諗咁多 比心機搵份工 收工打下炮就算 再諗落去你會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:14:59.000Z","msg":"喺香港，工字不出頭，做一世奴隸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過建議樓主研究吓證券市場好過，賭馬會點都係輸賠率<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855a310985f7c069ea497005277fdea187390ccf","tid":967510,"uid":126609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T02:28:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df546e916c269a9090956d451f630837bc897f83","tid":967510,"uid":13914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"賠率反映運氣及變數參與影響程度<br />\n馬的確可以用數據提高嬴錢機率, 但比波有更多不可控制因數, 諸如馬匹健康狀態, 陣上走位, 應該比波要更多運氣"},{"pid":"4c6f163e176d7e732a71082acf838c002ad41da3","tid":967510,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"樓主都係玩玩好了<br />\n唔希望多一個病態賭徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}